Description

trans-unit.source: Copies the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal" /> objects from this <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection" /> into the specified array, starting at the specified position index in array.
trans-unit.target: 배열에서 지정된 위치 인덱스부터 이 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal" />의 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection" /> 개체를 지정된 배열에 복사합니다.

trans-unit.source: `array` must be one-dimensional.
If it is not, an <xref:System.ArgumentException> is thrown.
Further exceptions are thrown if the number of elements to copy is greater than the available space from `index` to the end of `array`, if `array` is `null`, or if `index` is less than 0.
trans-unit.target: 복사할 요소의 수는 사용 가능한 공간 보다 큰 경우 추가 예외가 throw 됩니다 `index` 의 끝에 `array`경우 `array` 은 `null`, if 또는 `index` 0 보다 작습니다.

Removes the specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.UserPrincipal" /> object from the collection, and returns <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.UserPrincipal" /> was a member of this <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection" />, and <see langword="false" /> otherwise (in which case the method performs no operation).
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에서 지정된 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.UserPrincipal" /> 개체를 제거하고, <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.UserPrincipal" />이 이 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection" />의 멤버였으면 <see langword="true" />를 반환합니다. 그렇지 않으면 아무 작업도 수행하지 않고 <see langword="false" />를 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <see langword="bool" />.
This function can throw the following exceptions:
trans-unit.target: 이 함수는 다음과 같은 예외를 throw 할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Exception
Description

This method was called on the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.GroupPrincipal.Members> collection for a domain group, and the domain principal to be removed is a member of the group by virtue of its `primaryGroupId` attribute.
trans-unit.target: 이 메서드를 호출한는 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.GroupPrincipal.Members> 도메인 그룹과 도메인 보안 주체를 제거할 컬렉션 인해 그룹의 구성원은 해당 `primaryGroupId` 특성입니다.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext" /> object.
An <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.IdentityType" /> that identifies the format of <c>identityValue</c>.
A string.

Finds the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.UserPrincipal" /> object specified by the given <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext" /> and <paramref name="identityType" />/<paramref name="identityValue" /> pair from the collection, and returns <see langword="true" /> if the identified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal" /> was a member of this <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection" />, and <see langword="false" /> otherwise (in which case the method performs no operation).
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에서 특정 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext" /> 및 <paramref name="identityType" />/<paramref name="identityValue" /> 쌍으로 지정된 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.UserPrincipal" /> 개체를 찾고, 식별된 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal" />이 이 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection" />의 멤버였으면 <see langword="true" />를 반환하고, 그렇지 않으면 메서드에 대해 어떠한 작업도 수행하지 않고 <see langword="false" />를 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <see langword="bool" />.
This function can throw the following exceptions:
trans-unit.target: 이 함수는 다음과 같은 예외를 throw 할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Exception
Description

This method was called on the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.GroupPrincipal.Members> collection for a domain group, and the domain principal to be removed is a member of the group by virtue of its `primaryGroupId` attribute.
trans-unit.target: 이 메서드를 호출한는 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.GroupPrincipal.Members> 도메인 그룹과 도메인 보안 주체를 제거할 컬렉션 인해 그룹의 구성원은 해당 `primaryGroupId` 특성입니다.

trans-unit.source: No principal matching the specified parameters was found.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 된 매개 변수와 일치 하는 보안 주체가 없는 찾았습니다.

trans-unit.source: More than one principal matches the specified parameters.
trans-unit.target: 둘 이상의 보안 주체에 지정된 된 매개 변수와 일치합니다.

trans-unit.source: In theory, this should never happen, because <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection.Add%2A> throws an exception when there is an attempt to add duplicate principals to the collection.
trans-unit.target: 이론적으로, 경고, 때문에 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection.Add%2A> 컬렉션에 중복 된 보안 주체를 추가 하는 시도 하는 경우 예외를 throw 합니다.

trans-unit.source: However, it is possible that another API created the duplicate.
trans-unit.target: 그러나 다른 API 만들어 복제는 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: Thrown when `identityType` is an empty string.
Returns a synchronization object that can be used to synchronize access to this collection.
trans-unit.target: 이 컬렉션에 대한 액세스를 동기화하는 데 사용할 수 있는 동기화 개체를 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection" /> object itself.
The T:System.Array that should be populated with <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal" /> objects.
The position in <c>array</c> to which the first <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal" /> object should be copied to.

Copies the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal" /> objects from this <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection" /> into the specified array, starting at the specified position index in array.
trans-unit.target: 배열에서 지정된 위치 인덱스부터 이 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal" />의 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection" /> 개체를 지정된 배열에 복사합니다.

trans-unit.source: `array` must be one-dimensional.
If it is not, an <xref:System.ArgumentException> is thrown.
Further exceptions are thrown if the number of elements to copy is greater than the available space from `index` to the end of `array`, if `array` is `null`, or if `index` is less than 0.
trans-unit.target: 복사할 요소의 수는 사용 가능한 공간 보다 큰 경우 추가 예외가 throw 됩니다 `index` 의 끝에 `array`경우 `array` 은 `null`, if 또는 `index` 0 보다 작습니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns the count of Principal objects in this collection.
trans-unit.target: 이 컬렉션에 있는 보안 주체 개체의 수를 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns an <see langword="integer" />.
Always returns <see langword="false" />.
It is up to the application to synchronize access to this collection.
trans-unit.target: 이 컬렉션에 대한 액세스를 동기화하는 작업은 응용 프로그램에서 처리해야 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <see langword="bool" />.
Always returns `false`.
Returns a synchronization object that can be used to synchronize access to this collection.
trans-unit.target: 이 컬렉션에 대한 액세스를 동기화하는 데 사용할 수 있는 동기화 개체를 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection" /> object itself.
The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection" /> object.
Returns an enumerator to iterate through the principals in the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection" />의 보안 주체를 통해 반복하는 열거자를 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> containing the principals in the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection" />.
Conceptually, each instance of <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection> has a single enumerator associated with it.
trans-unit.target: 인스턴스마다 개념적으로 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection> 연관 열거자가 하나씩 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Although multiple calls to <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection.System%23Collections%23IEnumerable%23GetEnumerator%2A> return distinct <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator> objects, they share the same internal state.
trans-unit.target: 여러 번 호출 하지만 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalCollection.System%23Collections%23IEnumerable%23GetEnumerator%2A> 고유 반환 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator> 개체가 동일한 내부 상태를 공유 합니다.
